---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Base title="Terms of Use — LurraGrid">
  <Nav />

  <section class="pt-40 pb-20 px-8 md:px-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <p class="font-body text-xs tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-royal mb-6">Legal</p>
    <h1 class="font-display font-bold text-4xl text-frost mb-12">Terms of Use</h1>
    
    <div class="space-y-8 font-body text-sm text-frost-dim leading-relaxed">
      <p class="text-xs text-frost-dim">Last updated: May 2026</p>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-lg text-frost mb-3">General</h2>
        <p>This website is operated by LurraGrid. By accessing this site, you agree to these terms. The information provided on this site is for general informational purposes only and does not constitute an offer to sell securities or a solicitation of an offer to buy securities.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-lg text-frost mb-3">No Investment Solicitation</h2>
        <p>Nothing on this website constitutes investment advice or a solicitation of investment. Any investment offerings by LurraGrid are made exclusively through formal documentation, including a Private Placement Memorandum, to qualified accredited investors pursuant to applicable securities laws. Do not make investment decisions based solely on information contained on this site.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-lg text-frost mb-3">Forward-Looking Statements</h2>
        <p>This website may contain forward-looking statements regarding LurraGrid's business, technology, and market opportunity. These statements involve risks and uncertainties. Actual results may differ materially from those expressed or implied. LurraGrid undertakes no obligation to update forward-looking statements.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-lg text-frost mb-3">Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>All content on this site, including the LurraCascade Continuity System described herein, is protected by applicable intellectual property laws. The LurraCascade Continuity System is patent pending. LurraGrid, LurraCore, LurraCascade, LurraCharge, LurraBridge, LurraPDA, and LurraAtlas are proprietary names of LurraGrid.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-lg text-frost mb-3">Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>LurraGrid makes no warranties regarding the accuracy or completeness of information on this site. To the fullest extent permitted by law, LurraGrid shall not be liable for any damages arising from use of or reliance on information contained on this site.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-lg text-frost mb-3">Contact</h2>
        <p>Questions regarding these terms may be directed to <a href="mailto:ja@lurragrid.com" class="text-royal hover:text-royal-light transition-colors">ja@lurragrid.com</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Base>
